# Career Connections Overview

#### The <a href="https://courseinfo.code.org/csaif/" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Computer Science and AI Foundations Curriculum</a> integrates career exploration and emerging technologies as students develop foundational skills in computing.

#### Throughout the course, students engage with real-world case studies, hands-on projects, and industry-relevant tools to see how computer systems apply across various fields. 


---

