<h4>
In <b>Computer Systems and Devices, </b> several lessons are labeled with a <span style="background-color: lightgray; padding: 2px;"><b> 🧑‍🎓 Career Journeys </b></span>  tag indicating that the lesson connects to real-world careers.  
</h4> 

